  "reference_number": "RUS1030",
  "remarks": "\nAlexander Alexandrovich MIKHEEV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulation 2019 on the following grounds: MIKHEEV is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or equivalent of a Government of Russia-affiliated entity.\n",
